# Backend (Developed in Js with ExpressJs)

## We utilized the following libraries in our project:
<ul>
<li><strong> Express: </strong> Our chosen framework library for building our web application </li>
<li><strong> BcryptJs: </strong> Used for securely hashing user credentials to enhance security </li>
<li><strong> JSON web token: </strong> Employed for issuing authentication tokens, making the authentication process easier and more secure</li>
<li><strong> content-based-recommender: </strong> Integrated for recommending and serving personalized feeds on the homepage, enhancing the user experience. </li>
</ul>

